## Never / Always (Ch 8–9, 22)

**Never:** dashboard · workflow · module · launch · loading · achievement pop-ups  
**Shari never:** "Launching…" "Opening…" "Activating…"  
**Always:** conversation first · beauty before information · home wins

## Chapter 23 — Spark Estate Test (10 yeses)

Home? · Relationship? · Less stress? · Beauty? · Curiosity? · Simplicity? · Real estate? · Memorable? · Seen/encouraged? · Alive if removed?

**Most no → does not belong.**

## Objects & books (Ch 10–17)

Treasured possessions — Guidebook, Discovery Key, Cards, Accomplishments, Bell, Library volumes. Not UI.

## Before code

Read canon chapter for the place/object. Write `bible/rooms/` or `bible/objects/` page. Pass Ch 23.
